---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — Kilujo" description="Kilo, Kujo, Gianna & Stephen — our story.">
  <article class="prose about">
    <p class="about__eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1 class="about__title">K&nbsp;I&nbsp;L&nbsp;U&nbsp;J&nbsp;O</h1>

    <p class="about__lede">
      Mid-West meets East Asia. Quiet Kentucky farmlands, steeped in generations of
      family history, intertwine with the vibrant pulse of San Francisco, echoing
      tales of Taiwan and Southern China.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our journeys, both geographic and personal, paint a canvas as diverse as our
      family. Kilo, our spirited but selectively affectionate Shiba Inu, joined us
      during our travels through Nebraska, while Kujo, our Jindo/Border Collie mix,
      found his way into our hearts all the way from Korea.
    </p>

    <p>
      This is our story, captured through the lens of our everyday adventures, the
      connections we make between cultures, and the simple beauty we discover along
      the way.
    </p>

    <p class="signature">— Kilo, Kujo, Gianna &amp; Stephen</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about__eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .about__title {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .about__lede {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
